Program: Outlook
Title: Outlook Weekend: The Mountain Between Us
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/w3cswt5q
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 6 May 2018
In the 1990s, Alex Lowe and Conrad Anker were earning reputations as some of the best mountain climbers in the world. Jenni, Alex's wife, was a constant support. But after a fateful expedition on a mountain in Tibet, these three lives would become connected in a way they couldn't even imagine. (Photo: Ice Climber Scales a Glacier. Credit: Sandra Behne / Bongarts / Getty Images) Show less